messages.content: 9-1-1, what's your emergency?
Can I get a police on Dryden, Park, and Dewey?
They just jumped my 13-year-old daughter, and it's about to be all hell.
Is your daughter injured?
No, she has a scratch on her face under her chin.
Does she know who jumped her?
Yeah, she knows who jumped her.
How many people jumped her?
She said a whole bunch of grown women.
And where are they now?
I don't know, maybe eight or nine. I'm not sure.
Are they still near you?
No, they're not around.
Where exactly are you right now?
We’re at the corner of Dewey and Driving Park.
Are you and your daughter safe at the moment?
Yes, we are just standing on the corner.
What's your name?
My name is Tasha.
Is there any business or landmark nearby?
It's a one-way street, and they were standing out with six and nines.
Okay, stay where you are. Officers are on their way.
